'''Santo Domingo Savio''' is the fourth and last station on line K of the [[Medellín Metro]],<ref name="Escobar2010">{{cite book|author=Luis Fernando González Escobar|title=Ciudad y arquitectura urbana en Colombia 1980-2010|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=UjYa6z99nikC&pg=PA102|year=2010|publisher=Universidad de Antioquia|isbn=978-958-714-382-9|pages=102}}</ref> and the first station on line L. It is located in the northeast of [[Medellín]]. The station is named after [[Dominic Savio]].

